msgid ""
"Compatibility, rehearsal, upgrade, validation, and rollback procedures "
"for Klein for Ray jobs."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 作业的兼容性、演练、升级、验证和回滚流程。"

msgid "Upgrade Klein jobs"
msgstr "升级 Klein 作业"

msgid ""
"Upgrading a long-running Klein job means replacing its application "
"artifact, Klein/Ray environment, or graph while deciding whether its "
"checkpointed source positions, managed state, timers, and prepared sink "
"transactions remain compatible."
msgstr ""
"升级长期运行的 Klein 作业意味着替换其应用构件、Klein/Ray 环境或图，同时判断检查点记录的数据源位置、托管状态、定时器和已预备的 "
"Sink 事务是否仍然兼容。"

msgid ""
"Klein is currently `0.1.0.dev0` alpha software. Before 1.0, Semantic "
"Versioning compatibility is not promised, only the latest release is "
"eligible for security fixes, and checkpoint formats can change between "
"releases. Klein currently ships no automatic checkpoint migration tool "
"and no user-triggered command for creating an independently named "
"savepoint."
msgstr ""
"Klein 当前是 `0.1.0.dev0` alpha 软件。1.0 "
"之前不承诺语义化版本兼容性，只有最新版本符合获得安全修复的条件，而且检查点格式可能在版本之间发生变化。Klein "
"目前既没有自动检查点迁移工具，也没有用于创建独立具名 savepoint 的用户触发命令。"

msgid ""
"The supported maintenance path is a controlled stop and new submission "
"from a completed checkpoint. Replacing packages in live Ray actors, "
"mixing Klein versions within one job, or performing a rolling worker-by-"
"worker framework upgrade is not supported."
msgstr ""
"受支持的维护路径是受控停止，然后从已完成的检查点重新提交。不支持替换运行中 Ray actor 内的软件包、在一个作业内混用 Klein "
"版本，或逐个 worker 滚动升级框架。"

msgid "Check the version boundary"
msgstr "检查版本边界"

msgid "The current tested compatibility target is:"
msgstr "当前经过测试的兼容性目标为："

msgid "Python 3.10--3.12;"
msgstr "Python 3.10--3.12；"

msgid "`ray>=2.56.1,<2.57` with the `data` extra;"
msgstr "`ray>=2.56.1,<2.57`，并包含 `data` 可选依赖；"

msgid "`protobuf>=3.20.3,<7`;"
msgstr "`protobuf>=3.20.3,<7`；"

msgid "connector dependencies within the ranges in `pyproject.toml`."
msgstr "连接器依赖须处于 `pyproject.toml` 中声明的范围内。"

msgid ""
"Ray Data integration uses DeveloperAPI extension points. A newer Ray "
"minor is not supported merely because the package imports. Before "
"widening the Ray range, run the full unit, state, architecture, Ray "
"integration, SQL, and external-connector suites and review the "
"private/public API inventory. See [Compatibility](compatibility.md)."
msgstr ""
"Ray Data 集成使用 DeveloperAPI 扩展点。仅仅能够导入软件包，并不表示支持更新的 Ray 次版本。放宽 Ray "
"范围前，请运行完整的单元、状态、架构、Ray 集成、SQL 和外部连接器测试套件，并审查私有/公共 API "
"清单。请参阅[兼容性](compatibility.md)。"

msgid ""
"Pin exact resolved versions and the worker image for an upgrade. A "
"dependency upgrade can change pickle import paths, connector protocols, "
"SQL planning, or native-library behavior even when the Klein version does"
" not change."
msgstr ""
"升级时请固定准确的解析版本和 worker 镜像。即使 Klein 版本不变，依赖升级也可能改变 pickle 导入路径、连接器协议、SQL "
"规划或原生库行为。"

msgid "Preserve the checkpoint contract"
msgstr "保留检查点契约"

msgid ""
"The current restore implementation accepts only its current versioned "
"checkpoint metadata and managed-state formats. It rejects an unknown "
"format instead of guessing a migration. Checkpoint metadata and "
"application state use pickle, so class/module availability is also part "
"of compatibility."
msgstr ""
"当前恢复实现只接受当前版本的检查点元数据和托管状态格式。它会拒绝未知格式，而不是猜测迁移方式。检查点元数据和应用状态使用 "
"pickle，因此类/模块是否可用也是兼容性的一部分。"

msgid "Review every dimension below before attempting a stateful restore."
msgstr "尝试有状态恢复前，请审查以下每个维度。"

msgid "Dimension"
msgstr "维度"

msgid "Compatible requirement"
msgstr "兼容性要求"

msgid "Unsafe or unsupported change"
msgstr "不安全或不受支持的变更"

msgid "Completed checkpoint"
msgstr "已完成的检查点"

msgid ""
"Restore from the full URI of one `chk-N` directory whose `_metadata` is "
"readable. Preserve every referenced state object in the job prefix."
msgstr "从 `_metadata` 可读的某个 `chk-N` 目录完整 URI 恢复。保留作业前缀中所有被引用的状态对象。"

msgid ""
"An incomplete directory, only a copied `_metadata` file, edited pickle "
"metadata, or an object whose checksum/size no longer matches."
msgstr "不完整目录、只复制的 `_metadata` 文件、编辑过的 pickle 元数据，或校验和/大小不再匹配的对象。"

msgid "Graph identity"
msgstr "图标识"

msgid ""
"Rebuild streams in the same construction order and preserve sources, "
"stateful operators, sinks, names, partition edges, and chaining-sensitive"
" layout. After registering the terminals, save and compare "
"`ray.klein.explain(\"<job-name>\")` output."
msgstr ""
"按相同构建顺序重建流，并保留数据源、有状态算子、Sink、名称、分区边以及对算子链敏感的布局。保存并比较 "
"注册终结操作后的 `ray.klein.explain(\"<job-name>\")` 输出。"

msgid ""
"Adding, removing, or reordering even a stateless stream can shift "
"downstream numeric operator IDs. A same-numbered but different operator "
"can receive the wrong checkpoint entry."
msgstr "即使添加、删除或重新排序一个无状态流，也可能改变下游算子的数字 ID。编号相同但含义不同的算子可能收到错误的检查点条目。"

msgid "Managed state"
msgstr "托管状态"

msgid ""
"Preserve `state.keyed.max-parallelism`, descriptor names, key "
"type/serialization, value shape/serializer, namespaces, timer "
"representation, and stateful operator meaning."
msgstr ""
"保留 `state.keyed.max-"
"parallelism`、描述符名称、键类型/序列化、值形态/序列化器、命名空间、定时器表示以及有状态算子的含义。"

msgid ""
"Changing max parallelism, renaming descriptors/classes/modules, "
"incompatible value or key serialization, or assuming arbitrary Python "
"objects will migrate automatically."
msgstr "更改最大并行度，重命名描述符/类/模块，使用不兼容的值或键序列化，或假定任意 Python 对象会自动迁移。"

msgid "State backend"
msgstr "状态后端"

msgid ""
"Keep `state.backend.type` and its dependency unchanged for the upgrade "
"unless a separately tested migration is provided. Node-local state "
"remains disposable; durable checkpoint data is authoritative."
msgstr "除非提供单独测试过的迁移，否则升级时保持 `state.backend.type` 及其依赖不变。节点本地状态仍可丢弃；持久检查点数据才是权威来源。"

msgid ""
"Treating a memory-to-RocksDB or RocksDB-to-memory change as a documented "
"migration path. Klein does not currently promise cross-backend restore."
msgstr "将 memory 到 RocksDB 或 RocksDB 到 memory 的变更视为已有文档支持的迁移路径。Klein 当前不承诺跨后端恢复。"

msgid "Ordinary concurrency"
msgstr "普通并发度"

msgid ""
"Keyed operator concurrency may change only when it remains at or below "
"the unchanged max parallelism and a rehearsal proves key-group "
"redistribution."
msgstr "只有在键控算子并发度不超过保持不变的最大并行度，且演练已证明键组能够重新分布时，才能更改该并发度。"

msgid ""
"Changing source or sink concurrency without connector-specific evidence, "
"or changing concurrency together with unreviewed topology and state-"
"schema changes."
msgstr "没有连接器特定证据就更改数据源或 Sink 并发度，或者在更改并发度的同时引入未经审查的拓扑和状态模式变更。"

msgid "Source state"
msgstr "数据源状态"

msgid ""
"Preserve source type, topic/table/path identity, consumer group, "
"partition/split interpretation, start policy, source class, and "
"checkpoint-state schema."
msgstr "保留数据源类型、topic/table/path 标识、消费者组、分区/split 解释、起始策略、数据源类和检查点状态模式。"

msgid ""
"Switching connectors or identities and expecting old offsets to be "
"translated. RocketMQ broker-managed progress cannot be rolled back by a "
"Klein checkpoint."
msgstr "切换连接器或身份，却期望旧 offset 自动转换。由 RocketMQ broker 管理的进度无法通过 Klein 检查点回滚。"

msgid "Sink transactions"
msgstr "Sink 事务"

msgid ""
"Preserve sink type, destination, transaction/idempotency scheme, "
"credentials, serializer, and the code needed to deserialize and commit "
"prepared committables."
msgstr "保留 Sink 类型、目标、事务/幂等方案、凭据、序列化器，以及反序列化并提交已预备可提交项所需的代码。"

msgid ""
"Restoring a checkpoint into a rehearsal with access to production sinks, "
"or changing sink semantics while a checkpoint contains prepared work. "
"Restore may retry a durable committable."
msgstr "将检查点恢复到能够访问生产 Sink 的演练环境，或者在检查点包含已预备工作时更改 Sink 语义。恢复可能重试已持久化的可提交项。"

msgid "Event time and SQL"
msgstr "事件时间和 SQL"

msgid ""
"Preserve timestamp units/types, watermark and idleness assumptions, state"
" TTL meaning, changelog schema, join/window keys, and UDF semantics "
"unless the change has an explicit data migration plan."
msgstr ""
"除非变更具有显式数据迁移计划，否则应保留时间戳单位/类型、水位线和空闲假设、状态 TTL 含义、changelog 模式、连接/窗口键以及 UDF"
" 语义。"

msgid ""
"A change that makes existing timers/state semantically wrong even if "
"deserialization succeeds."
msgstr "即使反序列化成功，也会使现有定时器/状态语义错误的变更。"

msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "配置"

msgid ""
"Use canonical keys and preserve recovery-critical values. Compare the "
"effective configuration, not only source defaults."
msgstr "使用规范键，并保留恢复关键值。比较有效配置，而不只是源码默认值。"

msgid ""
"Relying on an unknown or misspelled key: Klein retains unknown keys as "
"metadata but does not apply them."
msgstr "依赖未知或拼写错误的键：Klein 会将未知键保留为元数据，但不会应用它们。"

msgid "External effects"
msgstr "外部副作用"

msgid ""
"Preserve deduplication keys and identify effects produced between the "
"rollback checkpoint and the cutover."
msgstr "保留去重键，并识别回滚检查点与切换之间产生的副作用。"

msgid ""
"Assuming checkpoint restore reverses Kafka, SQL, Redis, RocketMQ, "
"console, or other already-visible external writes."
msgstr "假定检查点恢复会撤销 Kafka、SQL、Redis、RocketMQ、控制台或其他已经可见的外部写入。"

msgid ""
"There is no general “stateless edit is safe” rule because source and sink"
" checkpoint keys also depend on graph identity. For a job whose old state"
" can be discarded, start a fresh deployment without "
"`execution.savepoint.path` and explicitly accept the new source/output "
"semantics instead of pretending it is a compatible restore."
msgstr ""
"不存在通用的“无状态编辑是安全的”规则，因为数据源和 Sink 的检查点键也依赖图标识。对于可以丢弃旧状态的作业，请在不设置 "
"`execution.savepoint.path` 的情况下启动全新部署，并明确接受新的数据源/输出语义，而不要假装这是兼容恢复。"

msgid "Prepare the upgrade"
msgstr "准备升级"

msgid "Keep the following rollback bundle before touching the running job:"
msgstr "接触运行中的作业前，请保留以下回滚包："

msgid "old wheel/application and immutable worker-image digest;"
msgstr "旧 wheel/应用以及不可变的 worker 镜像摘要；"

msgid "complete dependency lock and Python/Ray versions;"
msgstr "完整的依赖锁和 Python/Ray 版本；"

msgid "canonical configuration with secret references, not secret values;"
msgstr "包含密钥引用而非密钥值的规范配置；"

msgid ""
"saved `ray.klein.explain(\"<job-name>\")` output for the fully registered"
" graph;"
msgstr "已保存的、针对完整注册图的 `ray.klein.explain(\"<job-name>\")` 输出；"

msgid ""
"job name, namespace, source identities, sink destinations, and checkpoint"
" root;"
msgstr "作业名、命名空间、数据源身份、Sink 目标和检查点根目录；"

msgid "exact URI of a completed pre-upgrade `chk-N` directory;"
msgstr "已完成的升级前 `chk-N` 目录的准确 URI；"

msgid "evidence that the checkpoint's referenced objects remain retained;"
msgstr "检查点所引用对象仍被保留的证据；"

msgid "duplicate reconciliation and external rollback procedures."
msgstr "重复项对账和外部回滚流程。"

msgid "Inspect the running job from an operations client:"
msgstr "从运维客户端检查运行中的作业："

msgid ""
"Confirm that the snapshot is not marked `dashboard_stale`, the job is "
"running, and a recent checkpoint completed within the RPO. Validate "
"`_metadata` with the object-store or filesystem tooling used by the "
"platform. Do not select `_latest` as the restore URI; record the resolved"
" `chk-N` directory."
msgstr ""
"确认快照未标记为 `dashboard_stale`、作业正在运行，且近期检查点在 RPO 内完成。使用平台采用的对象存储或文件系统工具验证 "
"`_metadata`。不要选择 `_latest` 作为恢复 URI；请记录解析后的 `chk-N` 目录。"

msgid ""
"`ray-klein stop` requests cancellation. It does **not** first create a "
"checkpoint or savepoint. If the recorded checkpoint is too old, leave the"
" job running until a newer periodic checkpoint completes. At least one of"
" `execution.checkpointing.trigger.interval-duration` and "
"`execution.checkpointing.trigger.interval-records` must be nonzero for "
"periodic progress."
msgstr ""
"`ray-klein stop` 会请求取消。它**不会**先创建检查点或 "
"savepoint。如果记录的检查点太旧，请让作业继续运行，直到更新的周期性检查点完成。要周期性推进，`execution.checkpointing.trigger"
".interval-duration` 和 `execution.checkpointing.trigger.interval-records` "
"至少有一个必须非零。"

msgid "Rehearse safely"
msgstr "安全演练"

msgid ""
"Run the exact candidate artifact in an isolated Ray cluster before "
"production:"
msgstr "投入生产前，请在隔离的 Ray 集群中运行完全一致的候选构件："

msgid ""
"Use the same Python/Ray versions, optional extras, graph, max "
"parallelism, serializers, and state scale expected at cutover."
msgstr "使用切换时预期采用的相同 Python/Ray 版本、可选依赖、图、最大并行度、序列化器和状态规模。"

msgid ""
"Replay representative production-shaped input into staging source "
"identities and build a staging checkpoint with the current version."
msgstr "将有代表性的、接近生产形态的输入重放到预发布数据源身份，并使用当前版本创建预发布检查点。"

msgid ""
"Upgrade from that checkpoint into isolated sinks and a new checkpoint "
"prefix. Do not give the rehearsal credentials for production "
"destinations."
msgstr "从该检查点升级到隔离的 Sink 和新检查点前缀。不要向演练环境提供生产目标的凭据。"

msgid ""
"Inject worker, coordinator, driver, and sink failures during and after "
"restore."
msgstr "在恢复期间和恢复后注入 worker、协调器、driver 和 Sink 故障。"

msgid ""
"Compare state-derived output, source position, watermarks, late records, "
"duplicate envelope, restore duration, and first checkpoint duration."
msgstr "比较状态派生输出、数据源位置、水位线、迟到记录、重复范围、恢复耗时和首个检查点耗时。"

msgid ""
"Stop the candidate and prove the old artifact can still restore the "
"retained old-version staging checkpoint."
msgstr "停止候选版本，并证明旧构件仍可恢复保留的旧版本预发布检查点。"

msgid ""
"Do not restore an untrusted checkpoint. Also avoid using a production "
"checkpoint as a harmless test fixture: it contains pickle payloads and "
"may contain prepared sink committables that recovery can retry. Generate "
"a production-shaped staging checkpoint with isolated connector "
"identities."
msgstr ""
"不要恢复不受信任的检查点。也不要把生产检查点当作无害的测试夹具：它包含 pickle 载荷，还可能包含恢复时会重试的已预备 Sink "
"可提交项。请使用隔离的连接器身份生成接近生产形态的预发布检查点。"

msgid "Perform the cutover"
msgstr "执行切换"

msgid "1. Freeze the deployment definition"
msgstr "1. 冻结部署定义"

msgid ""
"Prevent concurrent graph, image, configuration, schema, and connector "
"changes. Record the candidate digests and approved checkpoint URI."
msgstr "阻止同时发生的图、镜像、配置、模式和连接器变更。记录候选版本摘要和已批准的检查点 URI。"

msgid "2. Wait for the recovery point"
msgstr "2. 等待恢复点"

msgid ""
"Wait for a completed durable checkpoint and capture its exact `chk-N` "
"URI. Verify source lag, checkpoint duration, pending sink transactions, "
"and output health. A directory without `_metadata` is incomplete."
msgstr ""
"等待持久检查点完成，并获取其准确的 `chk-N` URI。验证数据源延迟、检查点耗时、待处理 Sink 事务和输出健康状况。缺少 "
"`_metadata` 的目录是不完整的。"

msgid "3. Stop the old job"
msgstr "3. 停止旧作业"

msgid ""
"Confirm terminal status and that old detached actors no longer serve "
"control requests. Stop external schedulers from resubmitting the old "
"artifact. Do not run old and new jobs concurrently against the same "
"consumer identity or non-idempotent destination."
msgstr "确认终止状态，并确认旧的分离 actor 不再处理控制请求。阻止外部调度器重新提交旧构件。不要让新旧作业使用相同的消费者身份或非幂等目标并发运行。"

msgid "4. Deploy one candidate environment"
msgstr "4. 部署单一候选环境"

msgid ""
"Roll out the immutable candidate to every eligible Ray node before "
"submission. Do not mix old and new Klein workers. If the Ray framework "
"itself changes, create a separately tested cluster rather than upgrading "
"live actors in place."
msgstr ""
"提交前，将不可变候选版本部署到每个符合条件的 Ray 节点。不要混用新旧 Klein worker。如果 Ray "
"框架本身发生变化，请创建单独测试过的集群，不要原地升级运行中的 actor。"

msgid "5. Restore explicitly"
msgstr "5. 显式恢复"

msgid "Build the compatible graph and set the complete checkpoint URI:"
msgstr "构建兼容的图并设置完整的检查点 URI："

msgid ""
"Use a fresh namespace when old actors may still exist or when a shadow "
"cluster must remain operationally distinct. After restore, new "
"checkpoints are written under the new namespace's job directory. Reusing "
"a stable namespace can retain the old operational identity, but only "
"after the old actors are confirmed gone. In both cases, "
"`execution.savepoint.path` must identify the approved checkpoint "
"explicitly."
msgstr ""
"旧 actor 可能仍然存在，或影子集群必须在运维上保持独立时，请使用新命名空间。恢复后，新检查点会写入新命名空间的作业目录。只有确认旧 "
"actor 已消失后，才能通过复用稳定命名空间保留旧运维标识。无论哪种情况，`execution.savepoint.path` "
"都必须显式指向已批准的检查点。"

msgid "6. Validate before declaring success"
msgstr "6. 验证后再宣布成功"

msgid "Require all of the following:"
msgstr "必须满足以下全部条件："

msgid "the job reaches and remains `RUNNING` without exhausting restart attempts;"
msgstr "作业到达并保持 `RUNNING`，且未用尽重启次数；"

msgid ""
"the graph/operator IDs and effective configuration match the reviewed "
"plan;"
msgstr "图/算子 ID 和有效配置与审查过的计划一致；"

msgid "restored source positions are near the recorded checkpoint;"
msgstr "恢复后的数据源位置接近记录的检查点；"

msgid ""
"keyed state, timers, SQL state, watermarks, and late-data behavior are "
"correct;"
msgstr "键控状态、定时器、SQL 状态、水位线和迟到数据行为正确；"

msgid ""
"output has no loss outside the documented source boundary and duplicates "
"are absorbed by the designed idempotency/reconciliation mechanism;"
msgstr "除已记录的数据源边界外，输出没有丢失，并且重复项被设计的幂等/对账机制吸收；"

msgid "prepared transactional output reaches the expected final state;"
msgstr "已预备事务输出达到预期最终状态；"

msgid "restore duration is inside the RTO;"
msgstr "恢复耗时在 RTO 以内；"

msgid "the first post-upgrade checkpoint completes and is readable;"
msgstr "升级后首个检查点完成且可读取；"

msgid ""
"checkpoint age, restart, lag, backpressure, state, replay, and sink-"
"failure alerts remain healthy through a soak period."
msgstr "在稳定性观察期内，检查点年龄、重启、延迟、反压、状态、重放和 Sink 失败告警持续健康。"

msgid ""
"Use `ray-klein status <new-namespace> --json`, retained logs, exported "
"metrics, and destination-level reconciliation. Successful submission "
"alone is not an upgrade success."
msgstr ""
"使用 `ray-klein status <new-namespace> "
"--json`、保留的日志、导出的指标和目标端对账进行验证。仅成功提交并不代表升级成功。"

msgid "Roll back"
msgstr "回滚"

msgid ""
"Roll back when restore fails, the job repeatedly recovers, state-derived "
"output is wrong, a connector cannot resume, or the candidate cannot "
"complete a new checkpoint."
msgstr "当恢复失败、作业反复进入恢复、状态派生输出错误、连接器无法恢复，或候选版本无法完成新检查点时，请回滚。"

msgid "Stop the candidate and disable its automatic resubmission."
msgstr "停止候选版本并禁用其自动重新提交。"

msgid "Prevent further candidate writes or requests to external sinks."
msgstr "阻止候选版本继续写入外部 Sink 或向其发送请求。"

msgid ""
"Preserve its logs, status snapshot, failed checkpoint paths, and "
"destination reconciliation evidence."
msgstr "保留其日志、状态快照、失败检查点路径和目标端对账证据。"

msgid ""
"Redeploy the exact old application, worker image, dependencies, "
"Ray/Python versions, graph, and configuration."
msgstr "重新部署完全相同的旧应用、worker 镜像、依赖、Ray/Python 版本、图和配置。"

msgid ""
"Restore the old artifact from the recorded **pre-upgrade** checkpoint, "
"not a checkpoint written by the candidate."
msgstr "从记录的**升级前**检查点恢复旧构件，而不是从候选版本写入的检查点恢复。"

msgid ""
"Validate source positions, state, sink effects, and completion of a new "
"old-version checkpoint."
msgstr "验证数据源位置、状态、Sink 副作用以及新的旧版本检查点是否完成。"

msgid ""
"Reconcile or deduplicate external effects produced since the rollback "
"point."
msgstr "对账或去重回滚点之后产生的外部副作用。"

msgid ""
"A rollback rewinds Klein state; it does not undo output already visible "
"in an external system. Kafka, SQL, Redis, RocketMQ, console, and custom "
"sinks can replay or retain effects according to their documented "
"guarantees. Filesystem, Iceberg, and correct two-phase sinks have "
"stronger checkpoint publication boundaries, but destination-specific "
"validation is still required."
msgstr ""
"回滚会倒退 Klein 状态，但不会撤销外部系统中已经可见的输出。Kafka、SQL、Redis、RocketMQ、控制台和自定义 Sink "
"可能按照其已记录的保证重放或保留副作用。文件系统、Iceberg 和正确实现的两阶段 Sink "
"具有更强的检查点发布边界，但仍需要针对具体目标进行验证。"

msgid ""
"Never assume an old release can read a checkpoint created by a newer "
"alpha release. Keep the pre-upgrade checkpoint, its referenced objects, "
"and the old artifact until the candidate has passed the agreed soak "
"period and rollback window."
msgstr ""
"绝不要假定旧版本能够读取较新 alpha "
"版本创建的检查点。在候选版本通过约定的稳定性观察期和回滚窗口之前，请保留升级前检查点、其引用的对象和旧构件。"

msgid "Upgrade decision matrix"
msgstr "升级决策矩阵"

msgid "Proposed change"
msgstr "拟议变更"

msgid "Default decision"
msgstr "默认决策"

msgid ""
"Patch within the pinned application dependencies, no state, graph, or "
"connector change"
msgstr "固定的应用依赖范围内的补丁，且不更改状态、图或连接器"

msgid ""
"Rebuild and run the full relevant test tiers; still perform a normal "
"stop/resubmit."
msgstr "重新构建并运行所有相关测试层级；仍需执行正常的停止/重新提交。"

msgid "Klein release change with stateful restore"
msgstr "进行有状态恢复的 Klein 版本变更"

msgid ""
"Rehearsal and explicit checkpoint compatibility proof required. No "
"default compatibility promise before 1.0."
msgstr "需要演练并明确证明检查点兼容性。1.0 之前不提供默认兼容性承诺。"

msgid "Ray 2.56 patch change inside the declared range"
msgstr "声明范围内的 Ray 2.56 补丁版本变更"

msgid ""
"Test the resolved patch on every supported Python version and run Ray "
"integration/connector suites."
msgstr "在每个受支持的 Python 版本上测试解析后的补丁版本，并运行 Ray 集成/连接器测试套件。"

msgid "Ray minor outside `>=2.56.1,<2.57`"
msgstr "`>=2.56.1,<2.57` 范围之外的 Ray 次版本"

msgid ""
"Unsupported until the project widens the declared range after API review "
"and CI."
msgstr "在项目经过 API 审查和 CI 后放宽声明范围之前，不受支持。"

msgid "Python minor change"
msgstr "Python 次版本变更"

msgid ""
"Rebuild all native dependencies and prove pickle/state and connector "
"compatibility in rehearsal."
msgstr "重新构建所有原生依赖，并在演练中证明 pickle/状态和连接器兼容性。"

msgid "Add/remove/reorder an operator"
msgstr "添加/删除/重新排序算子"

msgid ""
"Treat as topology-incompatible unless an explicit migration and restore "
"test proves all checkpoint identities and semantics."
msgstr "除非显式迁移和恢复测试证明所有检查点标识及语义，否则按拓扑不兼容处理。"

msgid "Change keyed concurrency only"
msgstr "仅更改键控并发度"

msgid ""
"Permitted only at or below unchanged max parallelism, with connector "
"constraints and restore/rescale testing."
msgstr "只有在不超过保持不变的最大并行度，并满足连接器约束且完成恢复/扩缩测试时才允许。"

msgid ""
"Change max parallelism, state descriptor/serializer, checkpoint format, "
"or backend type"
msgstr "更改最大并行度、状态描述符/序列化器、检查点格式或后端类型"

msgid ""
"No automatic migration. Start without old state or implement and validate"
" a dedicated migration before cutover."
msgstr "没有自动迁移。请在不使用旧状态的情况下启动，或在切换前实现并验证专用迁移。"

msgid "Change source/sink type, identity, or delivery semantics"
msgstr "更改数据源/Sink 类型、身份或交付语义"

msgid ""
"Design a data migration and reconciliation procedure; checkpoint restore "
"alone is insufficient."
msgstr "设计数据迁移和对账流程；仅恢复检查点并不足够。"

msgid ""
"See [Checkpoint recovery](checkpoint-recovery.md) for restore mechanics, "
"[Delivery guarantees](delivery-semantics.md) for external effects, "
"[Security](security.md) for trusted checkpoint handling, and the "
"[Production readiness checklist](production-readiness.md) for the release"
" gate."
msgstr ""
"恢复机制请参阅[检查点恢复](checkpoint-recovery.md)，外部副作用请参阅[交付保证](delivery-"
"semantics.md)，受信任检查点处理请参阅[安全](security.md)，发布门槛请参阅[生产就绪检查清单](production-"
"readiness.md)。"
